our model.from sentence: We see empirically that our model outperforms all generative models on NarrativeQA , and is competitive with the top span prediction models .

NOIC commonsense integration.from sentence: Furthermore , with the NOIC commonsense integration , we were able to further improve performance ( p < 0.001 on all metrics 5 ) , establishing a new state - of - the - art for the task .

our model.from sentence: We also see that our model performs reasonably well on WikiHop , and further achieves promising initial improvements via the addition of commonsense , hinting at the generalizability of our approaches .

improvement.from sentence: We speculate that the improvement is smaller on Wikihop because only approximately 11 % of WikiHop data points require commonsense and because WikiHop data requires more fact - based commonsense ( e.g. , from Freebase ) as opposed to semantics - based commonsense ( e.g. , from Con-ceptNet ( Speer and Havasi , 2012 ) ) .
